@UnitConversionApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5299

### 1. Valid Length Conversion (Meter to Feet)
GET {{UnitConversionApi_HostAddress}}/api/conversion?value=100&from=meter&to=feet
Accept: application/json

### 2. Valid Temperature Conversion (Celsius to Fahrenheit)
GET {{UnitConversionApi_HostAddress}}/api/conversion?value=0&from=celsius&to=fahrenheit
Accept: application/json

### 3. Valid Weight Conversion (Kilogram to Pound)
GET {{UnitConversionApi_HostAddress}}/api/conversion?value=10&from=kilogram&to=pound
Accept: application/json

### 4. Invalid Unit Validation (Unsupported Unit)
GET {{UnitConversionApi_HostAddress}}/api/conversion?value=10&from=kilogram&to=stone
Accept: application/json

### 5. Incompatible Category Validation (Length to Temperature)
GET {{UnitConversionApi_HostAddress}}/api/conversion?value=100&from=meter&to=fahrenheit
Accept: application/json

### 6. Missing Parameter Validation (No Value Parameter)
GET {{UnitConversionApi_HostAddress}}/api/conversion?from=meter&to=feet
Accept: application/json

